      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce143",
      "text": ">[Hisui3718_sh https://x.com/Hisui3718_sh/status/1834064399608230047] divide",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce144",
      "text": "> #ひすい謎",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce145",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GXPadvEbIAA7R6b?format=png&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce146",
      "text": " わからない…[cak.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce147",
      "text": "  この❌はなんだろう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce148",
      "text": "  [~ 1が小さいので促音？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62e780000000000c8d043",
      "text": "   そう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1774595704,
      "updated": 1774595706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce149",
      "text": "  [~ だとすると❌は濁点？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62e7c0000000000c8d044",
      "text": "   そう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1774595708,
      "updated": 1774595711
    },
    {
      "id": "69c62c520000000000cce14a",
      "text": "  わかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774595154,
      "updated": 1774595154
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648ea0000000000d608e6",
      "text": " \t\tまだわからない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602475,
      "updated": 1774602479
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648ec0000000000d608e7",
      "text": "  \t\t[~ 小さい字がやゆよだとすると隣はまなので濁点はつかない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602476,
      "updated": 1774602479
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648ec0000000000d608e8",
      "text": "  \t\t[~ ちいさいつだとすると \"じっすし\"]意味がわからん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602476,
      "updated": 1774602479
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648ec0000000000d608e9",
      "text": "  \t\t[~ タイトルがdivideだから何かが分割されているのか？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602476,
      "updated": 1774602479
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648ec0000000000d608ea",
      "text": "   ヒント:[~ 答えのとこはアラビア数字なのにマス内はなぜわざわざローマ数字で書いてあるのか？あたりからとけた]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602476,
      "updated": 1774602478
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6463f0000000000d608e4",
      "text": "   \tわからない〜〜[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774601791,
      "updated": 1774601795
    },
    {
      "id": "69c646d40000000000f512eb",
      "text": "   \t [~ Ⅳが何と何からできているか考えるといけるかも][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1774601941,
      "updated": 1774601976
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6489b0000000000f60bb3",
      "text": "   \t あーー、なるほど、理解[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602395,
      "updated": 1774602403
    },
    {
      "id": "69c648db0000000000d608e5",
      "text": "   \t \t[~ 最終的に5ができるw]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774602459,
      "updated": 1774602465
